  <entry>
    <title>咖啡时光</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2021/09/17/%E5%B0%8F%E8%83%96/coffee/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2021/09/17/%E5%B0%8F%E8%83%96/coffee/</id>
    <published>2021-09-17T11:23:41.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-09-17T12:35:19.950Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>暑假后半月，和小胖开始了咖啡日常<br>天天神券，还真是天天神券<br>我们全用在了咖啡和轻食身上<br><img lazyload src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Xcloud1988/Pix@master/1223/IMG_0641.mrxbvkslahc.jpg"><br>Lowey的拿铁确实挺浓的，味很正，精神很振奋。<br><img lazyload src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Xcloud1988/Pix@master/1223/IMG_0681.6qix1g5qiww0.jpg"><br>这张是小胖的，有一说一，好看的。<br><img lazyload src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Xcloud1988/Pix@master/1223/IMG_0660.6p4i5gmp0a80.jpg"><br>@me的包装是一绝<br>和小胖有一杯白色的约定<br>味道偏淡些，但苦味正好。<br><img lazyload src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Xcloud1988/Pix@master/1223/IMG_0678.7h7q9hb1l400.jpg"><br>nowwa的桂花拿铁也还不错，相比之下我可能更喜欢晓风书屋的桂花拿铁<br>nowwa的桂花味更重些，把苦味遮了大半，会有种偏腻的感觉。<br><img lazyload src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Xcloud1988/Pix@master/1223/IMG_0679.5fmnjjk4jbk0.jpg"><br>当然，除了咖啡，还有奶茶。<br>校内奶茶店打卡。<br>无糖杨枝甘露不错的，<br>可惜我没摇开，前几口就把芒果吸完了。<br>导致后面几口喝的我清汤呱啦的。<br><img lazyload src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Xcloud1988/Pix@master/1223/IMG_0700.5uqrkt3l5u80.jpg"><br><img lazyload src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Xcloud1988/Pix@master/1223/IMG_0695.5qn62e5zy4w0.jpg"><br>陆羽的茶，喜欢！<br>是清淡的茶味，喝完留香，不腻，清甜。<br>据小胖说抹茶味也很正，下次要尝试。</p><p>那今日饮品频道就到这里了，日后会继续更新，加油加油加油</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
